name: CSS-Basics
format:
<style>

* {
    background: none;
}

    button, .color-picker-input {
        background: none !important;
    }

    root, a, button, p, div {
        -webkit-user-select: none !important;
    }

    md-switch .md-thumb {
    background-color: #ffe6e6 !important; /* circle color */
    }
    
    /* Change the switch background color (inactive state) */
    md-switch .md-bar {
    background-color: #660000 !important; /* darker color */
    }
    
    /* Optionally, change the switch background color when it's in the 'on' state */
    md-switch.md-checked .md-bar {
    background-color: #660000 !important; /* keep the same color when on */
    }
    
    /* Optional: Adjust the checked thumb for better visibility */
    md-switch.md-checked .md-thumb {
    background-color: #ffe6e6 !important; /* keep the same color when toggled on */
    }

    /* Change slider thumb (circle) */
    md-slider .md-thumb:after {
    background-color: #ffe6e6 !important; /* Inner circle color */
    border: 2px solid #ffe6e6 !important; /* Outer border color */
    width: 24px !important; /* Adjust width (make it larger or smaller as needed) */
    height: 24px !important; /* Adjust height (make it larger or smaller as needed) */
    border-radius: 50% !important; /* Make sure it's fully round */
    }
    
    /* Change the bar (track) when inactive */
    md-slider .md-track {
    background-color: #660000 !important;
    }
    
    /* Change the bar (track) when active / filled portion */
    md-slider .md-track-fill {
    background-color: #660000 !important;
    }

    body * {
    color: #ffe6e6; /*!important/*
    fill: black !important; /* For SVGs and icons */
    }

    body {
        /*background-image: url("http://192.168.178.1:1880/ui/2023.jpg");*/
        /*background: linear-gradient(rgba(40, 42, 49, 1.0) 40%, rgba(47, 49, 56, 1.0) 80%) !important;*/
        /*background-size: cover !important;*/

        background: -webkit-linear-gradient(
            55deg,
            #cc0000 0%,
            #1a0000 100%
        ) !important;
        
        -webkit-touch-callout: none !important;
        color: #330000 !important;
        padding-top:5px !important;
    }
    
    body.nr-dashboard-theme md-toolbar,
    body.nr-dashboard-theme md-content md-card {

    }

    
    ui-card-panel {
        background-color: rgba(250,250,250,0.3) !important;
        border:none !important;
        border-radius: 10px !important;
/*        box-shadow: 0 3px 6px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19) !important;
*/    }

    ui-card-panel>div.nr-dashboard-cardpanel>div>md-card {
        background: none !important;
    }
    ui-card-panel>div.nr-dashboard-cardpanel button {
        /*background: none !important;*/
    } 
    md-toolbar {
        background: none !important;
    }
    md-sidenav {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(40, 42, 49, 0.90) 20%, rgba(47, 49, 56, 0.90) 80%) !important;
    }
    md-card.nr-dashboard-button * {
        box-shadow: none !important;
    }
    md-card.nr-dashboard-template * {
        background: none !important;
    }
    .md-text {
        color: black;
    }
    .nr-dashboard-cardtitle {
        color: white !important;
    }
    label {
        color: white !important;
    }
    input {
        color: white !important;
    }

</style>
